headline: Paychex (NasdaqGS:PAYX) Increases Dividend by 10% to US$1.08 Per Share
summary: Paychex (NasdaqGS:PAYX) saw a price increase of 1.66% over the last week, influenced by the company's announcement of a dividend increase, reflecting its commitment to shareholder value. This move added weight to the overall market's positive trend, which rose 1.8% due to strong jobs data and potential trade talks between the U.S. and China. Although the broader market's optimism was driven by these macroeconomic developments, Paychex's dividend announcement aligned with the overall positive...

headline: Paychex Declares a 10% Increase to Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., May 02, 2025--The Board of Directors of Paychex, Inc. declared a regular quarterly cash dividend on Paychex common stock of $1.08 per share, an increase of $0.10 (or 10%) from the prior quarterly dividend of $0.98 per share, payable on May 29, 2025 to shareholders of record as of May 12, 2025.
